+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013kdFeKnkQmrSxNwCMovcbq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Non-interactive mode: using Autopilot. The task is well-specified — this is a document management API with clear requirements. Let me make design decisions quickly and move to implementation.\n\n**Key design decisions (autopilot):**\n\n1. **Route structure**: Standard REST — `/auth/register`, `/auth/login`, `/folders`, `/documents`, `/share`, `/activity`\n2. **Auth**: Simple UUID-based tokens stored in a Map\n3. **Storage**: Maps keyed by UUID for users, folders, documents, shares\n4. **File structure**: Single `src/app.ts` with modular route handlers — simple enough for in-memory API\n5. **Permission model**: Share records with role enum, effective permission = most permissive across all paths\n6. **Folder permission inheritance**: Sharing a folder grants access to all documents within it\n\nLet me skip the formal design document and go straight to TDD since the requirements are fully specified."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":165,"cache_read_input_tokens":23910,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":165},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e0e56e61-6d3a-4673-8e92-d545b74e6b81","uuid":"3cd3c723-bb2a-4785-b709-937a636a542c"}
